name: DRVR NOT LVR
description:
Cliff Blank | Community Pool Drop

We would need a license to love, there would be fewer lines, fewer misunderstandings but definitely more accidents. 
The arteries of our heart would be 4 lanes so that we could reach love in a short time. Of course, there could always be works and exits closed but at least we would have fewer surprises and we would react accordingly, choosing another exit or deciding to continue on our way.
